==English==
===Etymology===
(Greek) ''halo'', salt, ''gen'', produce
===Noun===
'''halogen'''
# in [[chemistry]], any [[element]] of group 7, i.e. [[fluorine]], [[chlorine]], [[bromine]], [[iodine]], [[astatine]].

===Related terms===
*[[halide]]
*[[quartz halogen lamp]]

